696
00:41:47.640 --> 00:41:51.200
Can you say a little bit more about how the CCR8 scoring

697
00:41:51.260 --> 00:41:53.500
was done? In particular,

698
00:41:54.540 --> 00:41:56.980
did you also look at FoxP3,

699
00:41:58.300 --> 00:41:59.410
since not all

700
00:42:00.520 --> 00:42:03.880
Treg cells are... While CCR8 is very

