00:42:03.920 --> 00:42:04.530
selective

702
00:42:05.360 --> 00:42:09.269
for Treg cells relative to other T cells in

703
00:42:09.300 --> 00:42:10.320
the tumor,

704
00:42:11.560 --> 00:42:15.420
not all Treg cells are CCR8 positive.

705
00:42:16.140 --> 00:42:18.900
Yeah, no, excellent question. So the IPS score was

706
00:42:20.480 --> 00:42:24.320
basically based on the percentage of immune cells per field

707
00:42:24.380 --> 00:42:28.280
of view, and a minimum of four fields of views were

