00:42:28.400 --> 00:42:32.330
used on this study and up to 12, and if there's not enough, it was also allowed to

709
00:42:32.400 --> 00:42:33.260
be expanded.

710
00:42:34.340 --> 00:42:36.280
So that's how the IPS score was

711
00:42:37.400 --> 00:42:41.164
basically derived.And I don't have

