00:42:47.644 --> 00:42:51.504
intratumorally there's also some reduction in FOXP3,

715
00:42:51.604 --> 00:42:53.744
but that work is still ongoing,

716
00:42:54.564 --> 00:42:56.044
so further details will come.

717
00:42:57.644 --> 00:42:58.744
Go to that side.

718
00:42:59.164 --> 00:43:00.744
Yeah. So fascinating data.

719
00:43:01.604 --> 00:43:04.484
Question on the patient that had the partial response.

