00:43:39.404 --> 00:43:42.124
into, and others who did not, but I don't have that data.

731
00:43:43.624 --> 00:43:46.804
I have to get back with you on that particular patient with melanoma.

732
00:43:46.934 --> 00:43:46.934
Thank you.

733
00:43:46.944 --> 00:43:50.704
But the reality is 40% of the patients were pre-treated

734
00:43:51.244 --> 00:43:55.024
with PD-1 therapy. So, still the response rates are

