736
00:43:55.964 --> 00:43:56.304
Yeah.

737
00:43:57.704 --> 00:43:58.464
That microphone.

738
00:43:59.104 --> 00:44:00.524
Hey, excuse me.

739
00:44:01.444 --> 00:44:05.244
It was rather interesting that there was a lack of immune-related

