00:45:20.184 --> 00:45:23.604
Yeah. That'll be very interesting to addressing some of those issues. Thank you.

762
00:45:24.544 --> 00:45:25.644
We'll go to the middle microphone.

763
00:45:26.264 --> 00:45:29.864
So more globally, CCR8 depleting antibodies have been in the

764
00:45:29.944 --> 00:45:31.924
clinic for over five years.

765
00:45:32.884 --> 00:45:36.824
Some have shown greater anti-tumor activity than what we saw here, but

766
00:45:36.984 --> 00:45:40.004
none have advanced to later stage clinical trials.

