00:50:30.248 --> 00:50:32.328
So what is alveolar soft part sarcoma?

851
00:50:32.568 --> 00:50:36.468
It's extremely rare sarcoma that occurs in less than 1%

852
00:50:36.588 --> 00:50:38.568
