857
00:50:53.668 --> 00:50:56.968
Most of the tumors are resected upfront as management,

858
00:50:57.948 --> 00:51:01.748
but this tumor has a very high metastatic potential

859
00:51:01.828 --> 00:51:04.518
and can recur very late after resection,

860
00:51:05.768 --> 00:51:09.088
usually will occur in the lung, CNS, or bone.

861
00:51:10.168 --> 00:51:12.768
