CFE3 fusion proteins.

863
00:51:16.888 --> 00:51:20.668
There are two specific types, type one and type two.

864
00:51:20.728 --> 00:51:23.508
In our study, actually, most of our patient had type one.

865
00:51:24.288 --> 00:51:26.088
Did that make a difference? It's not clear.

866
00:51:27.848 --> 00:51:28.528
Our study

867
