879
00:52:13.308 --> 00:52:16.568
If they go on the drug holiday, they were scanned every three month.

880
00:52:17.918 --> 00:52:21.508
The intent is that during that two years of drug holiday, if their tumor

881
00:52:21.608 --> 00:52:24.688
recurs, they were given the option to resume

882
00:52:25.028 --> 00:52:26.068
