883
00:52:27.468 --> 00:52:31.408
At the end of two-year drug holiday, we weren't clear what to do at that point.

884
00:52:31.508 --> 00:52:35.448
We actually amended the study to follow patients

885
00:52:35.508 --> 00:52:38.438
every six month with scans to see if they had recurred.

886
00:52:41.288 --> 00:52:45.108
This was a early therapeutic clinical trial network study.

887
00:52:45.528 --> 00:52:49.488
It took a lot of sites for us to accrue the patients that we

888
00:52:49.528 --> 00:52:50.768
