889
00:52:51.708 --> 00:52:53.308
We were very successful in it.

890
00:52:54.288 --> 00:52:58.208
The single-arm study with atezolizumab given at 1,200

891
00:52:58.228 --> 00:53:01.998
milligrams for adults, 15 milligrams per kilogram for

892
00:53:02.088 --> 00:53:02.508
